# Hardware Documentation

This directory contains all hardware-related files for the Smart Energy Monitoring System.

## Contents

### Schematics
- Main circuit diagram
- Sensor connection diagrams
- Power supply circuit

### PCB Design
- KiCad project files
- Gerber files for manufacturing
- Bill of Materials (BOM)

### 3D Models
- Enclosure design files (STL format)
- Mounting brackets
- Sensor housing

## Component List

| Component | Quantity | Description |
|-----------|----------|-------------|
| ESP32 DevKit | 1 | Main microcontroller |
| ACS712 Current Sensor | 3 | 30A current measurement |
| ZMPT101B Voltage Sensor | 1 | AC voltage measurement |
| 16x2 LCD Display | 1 | Local readings display |
| 5V Power Supply | 1 | Power for the system |
| PCB | 1 | Custom designed circuit board |
| Enclosure | 1 | 3D printed protective case |

## Assembly Instructions

Detailed assembly instructions with photos will be added soon.

## Safety Considerations

⚠️ **WARNING**: This project involves working with mains electricity which can be dangerous. Always ensure power is disconnected before working on the circuit. Consider consulting a licensed electrician for installation.
